    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-01-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-01-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="643"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d643">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Chargé
                            <persName type="to">Garter</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-01-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 2, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 116.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have to acknowledge the receipt of your No.
                        103,<note n="a" xml:id="d643fna">Printed in <ref target="frus1905#pg_503"
                            >Foreign Relations, 1905, p. 503</ref>.</note> of the 13th ultimo, in
                    which, with reference to my telegram of December 15 to the <pb facs="0910"
                        n="804" xml:id="pg_804"/> ambassador on the subject of the boycott of
                    American goods by Chinese at Singapore, you transmit copy of a note from the
                    foreign office stating that the matter will be brought to the attention of the
                    governor of the Straits Settlements.</p>
                <p>This Government highly appreciates the action of the foreign office.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Elihu Root.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
